-ke-hinh-anh-dep-quang-cao-tren-facebook-thiet-ke-hinh-anh-mien-bac.html\/#31_Voi_hinh_anh_co_van_ban\" title=\"3.1 V\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n\">3.1 V\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-hinh-anh-quang-cao-tren-facebook-chuyen-nghiep-tai-ha-noi-thiet-ke-hinh-anh-dep-quang-cao-tren-facebook-thiet-ke-hinh-anh-mien-bac.html\/#32_Kich_thuoc_anh_chay_quang_cao\" title=\"3.2 K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\u00a0\">3.2 K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-hinh-anh-quang-cao-tren-facebook-chuyen-nghiep-tai-ha-noi-thiet-ke-hinh-anh-dep-quang-cao-tren-facebook-thiet-ke-hinh-anh-mien-bac.html\/#_33_Chi_nen_su_dung_1-2_font_khac_nhau_cho_hinh_anh\" title=\"\u00a03.3 Ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 1-2 font kh\u00e1c nhau cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\u00a0\">\u00a03.3 Ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 1-2 font kh\u00e1c nhau cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-hinh-anh-quang-cao-tren-facebook-chuyen-nghiep-tai-ha-noi-thiet-ke-hinh-anh-dep-quang-cao-tren-facebook-thiet-ke-hinh-anh-mien-bac.html\/#Voi_dich_vu_thiet_ke_anh_quang_cao_facebook_tai_A_Chau_Media_se_giup_ban_co_nhung_mau_thiet_ke_khien_ban_hai_long\" title=\"V\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5\u00a0thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\">V\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5\u00a0thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>Facebook hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng cao, do v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng facebook nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu h\u00fat ngo\u00e0i n\u1ed9i dung th\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u0169ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/em><\/p>\n<p><em>T\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t designe.<\/em><\/p>\n<p><em>B\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch\u00a0<strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook<\/strong> m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n? B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong><\/span> ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh theo \u00fd c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Vi_sao_lai_phai_thiet_ke_hinh_anh_quang_cao_tren_facebook\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>1. V\u00ec sao l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean facebook?\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Facebook (Facebook Ads) \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c\u00a0Marketing Online\u00a0ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. Ngo\u00e0i n\u1ed9i dung thu h\u00fat th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap m\u1eabu qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n, g\u00e2y \u00e2\u0301n t\u01b0\u01a1\u0323ng, ta\u0323o s\u01b0\u0323 chuy\u00ean nghi\u00ea\u0323p trong m\u0103\u0301t kha\u0301ch ha\u0300ng.<\/li>\n<li>Truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t: Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Thi\u00ea\u0301t k\u00ea\u0301 hi\u0300nh a\u0309nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1eb9p co\u0301 th\u00ea\u0309 la\u0300 chi\u0300a kho\u0301a \u0111\u00ea\u0309 gi\u01b0\u0303 ch\u00e2n kha\u0301ch ha\u0300ng. T\u0103ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i mua h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>Ta\u0323o s\u01b0\u0323 kha\u0301c bi\u00ea\u0323t so v\u01a1\u0301i \u0111\u00f4\u0301i thu\u0309 ca\u0323nh tranh tr\u00ean facebook<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0m \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook \u0111\u1eb9p \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u1eeb 30-70%, t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng comment inbox qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t\u00a0<strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook<\/strong>\u00a0s\u1ebd gi\u00fap chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng like fanpage facebook<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14496 \" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thiet_ke_hinh_anh_quang_cao_fb_tai_hn5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"959\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thiet_ke_hinh_anh_quang_cao_fb_tai_hn5.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thiet_ke_hinh_anh_quang_cao_fb_tai_hn5-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thiet_ke_hinh_anh_quang_cao_fb_tai_hn5-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 959px) 100vw, 959px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Doi_tuong_nen_thiet_ke_anh_quang_cao_facebook\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>2. \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb mu\u1ed1n qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m &#8211; d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhanh nh\u1ea5t, l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook s\u1ebd gi\u00fap qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb mu\u1ed1n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p>Doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ngu\u1ed3n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng cho nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Thiet_ke_anh_quang_cao_facebook_sao_cho_hieu_qua\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>3. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"31_Voi_hinh_anh_co_van_ban\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><strong>3.1 V\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n<\/strong><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ch\u1ea1y facebook ads c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a v\u0103n b\u1ea3n, ph\u1ea7n v\u0103n b\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 20% t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 khung h\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u1eb1ng 0.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, khi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng logo c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a v\u0103n b\u1ea3n, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ph\u00f3ng to qu\u00e1 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sai nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a facebook. C\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh cho m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14494 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thiet_ke_hinh_anh_quang_cao_fb_tai_hn3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1028\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"32_Kich_thuoc_anh_chay_quang_cao\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><strong>3.2 K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\u00a0<\/strong><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Khi\u00a0<strong>t\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Facebook<\/strong>, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb. \u1ea2nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. Ngo\u00e0i ra b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_33_Chi_nen_su_dung_1-2_font_khac_nhau_cho_hinh_anh\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><strong>\u00a03.3 Ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 1-2 font kh\u00e1c nhau cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\u00a0<\/strong><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u font kh\u00e1c nhau trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem kh\u00f3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u00edt font ch\u1eef s\u1ebd gi\u00fap th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-14491 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thiet_ke_hinh_anh_quang_cao_fb_tai_hn.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"754\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Voi_dich_vu_thiet_ke_anh_quang_cao_facebook_tai_A_Chau_Media_se_giup_ban_co_nhung_mau_thiet_ke_khien_ban_hai_long\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>V\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5\u00a0thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/p>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb &#8211; h\u1ee3p l\u00fd<\/p>\n<p>Nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u2013 Ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i<\/p>\n<p>Chuy\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean facebook t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o facebook \u0111\u1eb9p &#8211; \u00a0chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb\u00a0<strong>200k<\/strong>, v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1\u00a0<strong>5-<\/strong><strong>15%<\/strong> khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e3y nh\u1ea5c m\u00e1y v\u00e0 g\u1ecdi cho \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Facebook hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng cao, do v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng facebook nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu h\u00fat ngo\u00e0i n\u1ed9i dung th\u00ec h\u00ecnh&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":14496,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[59,77,57],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Facebook chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i - \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media Digital Marketing<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Chuy\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean facebook t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, uy t\u00edn, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-hinh-anh-quang-cao-tren-facebook-chuyen-nghiep-tai-ha-noi-thiet-ke-hinh-anh-dep-quang-cao-tren-fa